HEADWORD: Accentuation
<hw>Ac*cen`tu*a"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>accentuatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>accentuation</ets>.]</ety> <def>Act
of accentuating; applications of accent.</def> Specifically
